<% title "About" %>

<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Welcome to Sourcemod Translator!</h1>
  <p>This application allows plugin developers to upload Phrase files from plugins, and other users can add translations for languages they are fluent in.
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= link_to "Get Started!", "/auth/steam", :class => "btn btn-primary btn-large" %>
  </p>
</div>


<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Translators</h2>
    <p>
      Are you bilingual? Do you enjoy helping others in the community?
      You can help internationalize plugins by adding translations for phrases.
    </p>
    <p><%= link_to "Get started", "/auth/steam", :class => "btn" %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Developers</h2>
    <p>
      Want to support multiple languages in your plugin, but only know English?
      Upload your plugin and let others add translations!
    </p>
    <p><%= link_to "Get started", "/auth/steam", :class => "btn" %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Moderators</h2>
    <p>
      Are you a grammar nazi? Do you have extra time? 
      You can work as a moderator and modify submitted translations to help provide plugin authors with the best translation possible.
    </p>
    <p><%= link_to "Get started", "/auth/steam", :class => "btn" %></p>
  </div>
</div>
